# 🌈 MB3D Prints

Welcome to **MB3D Prints**!

We're a mommy and kid team who love bringing ideas to life through 3D printing. From fun articulated animals to practical organizers and personalized gifts, every item is printed with care, one layer at a time.

## 🖨️ What We Offer

- Articulated animals
- Keychains
- Home organization
- Home décor
- Fidget toys
- Gifts
- Seasonal items
- Personalized items (on select products)
- Custom color options

## 💜 Our Mission

We want to create quality 3D printed products that make people smile while spending time together as a family doing something we love.

## ⚠️ Design Credits

Unless otherwise noted, the digital 3D models used to create our products were designed by talented independent creators. We purchase and maintain commercial licenses when required and follow each designer's licensing terms.

MB3D Prints is the manufacturer of the physical products but does not claim ownership of designs created by other artists.

